flowchart TD
    BT([Beneficiary Tracking]) --> View[View beneficiaries + by-program chart<br/>active · total distributed · pending]
    View --> Act{Action?}

    Act -- Enroll --> Enroll[Select resident + program<br/>status · last release date · total]
    Act -- Edit --> Edit[Update status / release / notes]
    Act -- Remove --> Remove[Delete beneficiary]
    Act -- Manage programs --> Prog[Add program / deactivate program]
    Act -- Import --> Imp[Upload XLSX] --> ParseB[Parse & upsert]

    Enroll --> Save[Save to Supabase]
    Edit --> Save
    Remove --> Save
    Prog --> Save
    ParseB --> Save
    Save --> Refresh[Refresh registry + chart]
    Refresh --> Done([Return to Dashboard])
